{"tid":1921963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要求所有立法會參選人答香港法治是否已死","createTime":"2020-03-12T09:29:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T02:56:18.000Z","uid":26770,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3ee901eaf01d4bc39c781304592c700e7e4572dc","tid":1921963,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:29:53.000Z","msg":"香港法官係支持緊屈打成招<br />\n<ins>令到示威者遭強姦,打到傷殘的主謀</ins><br />\n<br />\n任何人反對法治已死就等同支持酷刑迫害異見者<br />\n大律師會同所有參選人係一定要答香港法治是否已死"},{"pid":"41e07ffcfe27552a6f63f8c418af73953c1cd383","tid":1921963,"uid":27416,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:31:38.000Z","msg":"到時蘋果吹雞告急叫你投公民黨你地敢唔投咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbfba98ab4aa25edab09612dd0e62d4d8e675f27","tid":1921963,"uid":18001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:35:05.000Z","msg":"需要更多權威人士宣揚香港只有人治"},{"pid":"08033ba36c88538ffb3c975774a8ac41d2e07635","tid":1921963,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41e07ffcfe27552a6f63f8c418af73953c1cd383","tid":1921963,"uid":27416,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:31:38.000Z","msg":"到時蘋果吹雞告急叫你投公民黨你地敢唔投咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:35:55.000Z","msg":"唔投咪唔投<br />\n國際上香港議題最重點就係警暴<br />\n<br />\n而香港法官係支持香港警魔通過打到人殘廢迫人認罪<br />\n香港法庭已干犯反人類罪行<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">任何人依然支持法官就當作共犯論,仲有咩資格做議員</span>"},{"pid":"9e2c76876fbaab2e4eb74f20afa50abea29d04c8","tid":1921963,"uid":44309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:57:00.000Z","msg":"我認同香港法治已死，但完全唔投票等於幫咗中共。"},{"pid":"761f687a38b4b0b3489f6c695415062fabaf1733","tid":1921963,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e2c76876fbaab2e4eb74f20afa50abea29d04c8","tid":1921963,"uid":44309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:57:00.000Z","msg":"我認同香港法治已死，